<main class="min-h-screen bg-brand-glacial text-brand-slate selection:bg-brand-aqua selection:text-white pt-32 pb-48">
  <div class="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-brand-aqua/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-brand-slate/5 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 relative z-10">
    <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-bold text-brand-aqua mb-4">Legal Policy</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-light mb-8 leading-tight">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-20">
      <div class="h-px w-8 bg-brand-aqua/40"></div>
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium text-brand-slate-light">Last Updated: June 2026</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-12 text-lg text-brand-slate-light font-medium leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-light text-brand-slate mb-6">What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you browse and use websites. They are used to enhance your experience by remembering your preferences and helping us understand how our clinical platform is being used.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-light text-brand-slate mb-6">How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          This Cookie Policy is issued by <strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">ELISENSE ENTERPRISE LLP</strong>, operating under the trademark <strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">SERAVOLVE™</strong>. We use cookies to provide a seamless and enhanced experience. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">Essential Cookies:</strong> Necessary for the operation of our shop, including secure checkout and account login.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">Performance Cookies:</strong> Helping us understand how users interact with our diagnostic tools and product library.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">Preference Cookies:</strong> Remembering your routine selections and preferences for future visits.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">Targeting Cookies:</strong> Providing you with relevant updates regarding our clinical synthesis and new product launches.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-light text-brand-slate mb-6">Managing Cookie Preferences</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          You have the right to choose whether to accept cookies. Most web browsers are set to accept cookies by default, but you can usually modify your browser setting to decline cookies if you prefer.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Please note that disabling cookies may affect the functionality of certain elements of the SERAVOLVE storefront, such as the Routine Builder and checkout stability.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-light text-brand-slate mb-6">Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our clinical platform or for legal and regulatory reasons.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-light text-brand-slate mb-6">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If you have any questions about our use of cookies, please contact us via:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">Email:</strong> info@seravolve.com</li>
          <li><strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">Phone/WhatsApp:</strong> +91 9978099097</li>
          <li><strong class="text-brand-slate font-bold">Address:</strong> 333 Shayona Plaza, Puna-Saroli Junction, BRTS Road, Surat, Gujarat 395010, India</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Legal Cookie Policy",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
